            <thetext>If you leave the browser window during a drag session with the mouse cursor  and release the mouse button there, the drag session will be cleared correctly.

But this is not true, if you run the application inside an iframe for following browser: Firefox 36.0, IE10 (10.0.9200.17229), IE11 (11.0.9600.17498), IE8 (8.0.6001.18702) und IE9 (9.0.8112.16421)

Recommend to clear the drag session if you release the mouse button inside an iframe, anyway.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
